{"tid":983692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 雖然冇再睇日劇，但覺得 長瀨智也 仲係個型男 🙄","createTime":"2019-01-16T07:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T15:03:14.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56b0861bd0bd1688855d3e500fb161a29141a4e4","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:22:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tLQxTi-Ot1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtLQxTi-Ot1w&d=ll1HIowsE26aSNlWinny49r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1f457a88\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tLQxTi-Ot1w</a><br />\n<br />\n依套係電影喎，佢冇再拍劇咩 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f8c432808d3958054d83dcaec9bded2d032f64d","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"一諗起mbmh d回憶又返晒黎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13a2a0107cbc095ff62f144bc3b81d461cdbd141","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"如果當時佢娶濱崎步你估會點 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44604ff48aecfd6f8dbea76ab5592de82d587a02","tid":983692,"uid":194690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:03:01.000Z","msg":"男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab70cf4c840252507619ce95e1cec24a3ea8c93","tid":983692,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"一個人的牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1410922d71e76e2b571c76a3ebb660eef7db91c4","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"傑尼斯男星長瀨智也剛滿40歲，正式邁入不惑之年。《週刊女性》報導，他4年前一時興起，在腹部紋下自己參與設計的紋身圖案，當時他對該紋身相當得意，還不時給朋友看，沒想到隨著年齡漸長，加上對日常生活造成不便，最近他又心生想要去除紋身的念頭，還可能因此花上一筆可觀的費用。"},{"pid":"a40c2d8610485685bab379ee954099c18f3ebba9","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"報導指出，他工作之餘很喜歡騎重型電單車，當時設計了一個由馬頭、螺絲與樹藤組合而成的圖案紋在腹部，由於該圖案象徵騎電單車的男人形象，他自己非常滿意，但這個圖案只紋在他身上4年，就讓他感到後悔了。據悉，他似乎已對該紋身失去新鮮感，加上也對平常生活帶來某些不便，他才又想藉雷射手術消除紋身。"},{"pid":"d0e6a63d8b2d006802504251fcc84310e8220ed5","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"長瀨以前與「步姊」濱崎步交往時，2人曾分別在右胸前和右後背紋下愛的紋身圖案，只要一前一後合體，就能組成心型圖案，可惜這段星戀情最後沒能開花結果，步姊後來也把右背紋身改成完整的心型圖案，與舊愛切割。"},{"pid":"f7ca424de1785e372f17945562af3c7708520dd0","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"當地整容業者表示，雷射去除紋身，每1公分正方形大小，費用約為1萬日圓，以長瀨的紋身為例，由於不確定他的大小，實際費用最少恐怕得花上120萬至150萬日圓，才能將紋身清除乾淨，費用不算便宜，若不想在日後去除圖案時再花冤枉錢，業者建議紋身前，最好還是考慮清楚再做決定。"},{"pid":"5f39b1504f80f0a2ffdf816db76db33c80d2ab3e","tid":983692,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一諗起mbmh d回憶又返晒黎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得有集搶布甸，跟住之後我就